ons Act (Ontario) and is registered in Ontario, ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CITLCE+TimesNewRomanPSMT", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 278332, "box": [62.12121212121212, 89.46964114987077, 843.3921565656565, 76.91862209302326], "id_box_line": 9, "box_line": [62.12121212121212, 149.8571188630491, 796.9339625420874, 16.531144379844932], "text": "Canada. The registered office of the company is Brookfield Place, 181 Bay Street, Suite 300, Toronto, Ontario, M5J 2T3.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/NGWESD+TimesNewRomanPSMT", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 278333, "box": [62.12121212121212, 214.6149899870801, 844.5887146464647, 31.627990633075], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [62.12121212121212, 214.6149899870801, 844.5887146464647, 16.531144379844932], "text": "These consolidated financial statements have been prepared in accordance with International Financial Reporting Standards ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CITLCE+TimesNewRomanPSMT", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 278333, "box": [62.12121212121212, 214.6149899870801, 844.5887146464647, 31.627990633075], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [62.12121212121212, 229.71183624031016, 521.5299566498317, 16.531144379844932], "text": "(\u201cIFRS\u201d) as issued by the International Accounting Standards Board (\u201cIASB\u201d).", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CITLCE+TimesNewRomanPSMT", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 278334, "box": [62.12121212121212, 250.76790536175713, 780.4426443602694, 16.531144379844932], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [62.12121212121212, 250.76790536175713, 780.4426443602694, 16.531144379844932], "text": "These financial statements were authorized for issuance by the Board of Directors of the company on March 28, 2014.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": 